# Contruo - Project Context

Contruo is an online SaaS platform for construction estimators to create, edit, and manage takeoffs. It supports real-time multi-user collaboration and will include AI-powered automation.

## Tech Stack

- **Frontend:** Next.js + React + TypeScript + Tailwind CSS + shadcn/ui
- **Backend:** FastAPI (Python 3.11+)
- **Database:** PostgreSQL via Supabase (with Row-Level Security)
- **Auth:** Supabase Auth (email/password)
- **Real-Time:** Liveblocks (live cursors, presence, measurement sync)
- **File Storage:** Supabase Storage (PDF plans, logos)
- **Payments:** DodoPayments (annual per-seat billing)
- **Task Queue:** Celery + Redis (PDF processing, exports, emails)
- **PDF Processing:** PyMuPDF (fitz) + pdfplumber

